Limit the roulette to duties of an appropriate difficulty based on the level of party members. The duty chosen will be within eight levels of the lowest level party member. For example, should the lowest character level in the party be 70, a duty ranging from level 63 to 70 will be chosen. The following requirements must be met to enable this option: ・Parties must meet minimum size requirements. ・Parties must meet entry requirements for two or more duties. ※Only the party leader's settings are applicable.

Revisit a dungeon in its completed state. Explorer Mode allows access to the following: ・Explorer Mode-exclusive actions ・Minions, mounts, and fashion accessories ・Changing jobs (excluding DoL/DoH classes) ・Performance actions ※Available only for selected duties completed by the player. ※Only the party leader's settings are applicable. ※Enabling Explorer Mode will disable all other Duty Finder participation requirement settings.
